<h2>Definitions and Statutory References</h2>
<p>Indecency with a child: Is defined by <a title="Section 21.11 Texas Penal Code" href="http://www.statutes.legis.state.tx.us/docs/pe/htm/pe.21.htm#21.11">&#167;21.11 Texas Penal Code</a>.</p>
<p>It means, in part, engaging in sexual activity with a child younger than 17 years of age who is not the actor's spouse unless the actor is not more than 3 years older than the victim and the victim is 14, 15, or 16 years of age. An offense may have occurred even if the child describes the activity as consensual.</p>


